The paper describes the design and control of a soft robot using machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of machine learning algorithms to discover effective gaits suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The robot's ability to demonstrate structural and behavioral resilience suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY). The use of machine learning algorithms also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.MA), and the paper's emphasis on discovering effective gaits suggests a focus on reinforcement learning (cs.LG).
